            <article class="post-preview">
    <a href="https://darcynorman.net/2023/08/01/building-a-mastodon-chatbot-with-chatgpt/">
        <h2 class="post-title">Building a Mastodon Chatbot With ChatGPT</h2>
        
        
        
    </a>

    <p class="post-meta">
        <span class="post-meta">
  
  
  <i class="fas fa-calendar"></i>&nbsp;August 1, 2023
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-clock"></i>&nbsp;5&nbsp;minutes
  
  
    &nbsp;|&nbsp;<i class="fas fa-book"></i>&nbsp;921&nbsp;words
  
  
  
</span>


    </p>
    <div class="post-entry">
        
        I had a random thought, triggered perhaps by the tinnitus that is constantly eeeeeeee-ing in the background of everything. What if there was a Mastodon bot that just replied to every toot that mentioned it, with a string of eeeeeee&rsquo;s of the same length as the message?
The second semi-random thought was that I had no idea how to even start to build such a thing.
The third obvious-in-2023 thought was that I&rsquo;d bet ChatGPT could help with this somehow.
        <a href="https://darcynorman.net/2023/08/01/building-a-mastodon-chatbot-with-chatgpt/" class="post-read-more">Read More</a>
        
        
        
		
		
			<hr><p><em>Images used in this post:</em></p>
		
		<a href="https://darcynorman.net/2023/08/01/building-a-mastodon-chatbot-with-chatgpt/">
		
				<img src="https://darcynorman.net/images/2023/2023-08-01-mastodon-bot-chatgpt-prompt.jpg" alt="screenshot of a prompt fed to ChatGPT: Build a Mastodon bot that replies to every message by converting the message into &ldquo;eeeeee&rdquo; of corresponding message length&quot;">
		
				<img src="https://darcynorman.net/images/2023/2023-08-01-tinnitus-bot-hello-world.jpg" alt="screenshot of 2 toots, one asking @tinnitus &ldquo;hey, tinnitus but. is this thing on?&rdquo; and the other responding &ldquo;eeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee&rdquo;">
		
				<img src="https://darcynorman.net/images/2023/2023-08-01-tinnitus-bot-mastodon-page.jpg" alt="screenshot of the Mastodon profile for Tinnutus Bot">
		
		</a>
		
    </div>

	
		<div class="blog-categories">
			
			  <a href="https://darcynorman.net/categories/general">general</a>&nbsp;
			
