				<img src="https://darcynorman.net/images/2016/ti-conversion-timelapse-thumbnail.webp" alt="poster image for video"  width="750" height="422" >
		
				<img itemprop="thumbnail" src="https://darcynorman.net/photos/2022/2022-05-01-tipi-taylor-institute.jpg" alt="Taken during the 2022 University of Calgary Conference on Postsecondary Learning and Teaching, hosted by the Taylor Institute for Teaching and Learning."/>
		
				<img itemprop="thumbnail" src="https://darcynorman.net/photos/2023/2023-02-16-new-artworking.jpg" alt="https://darcynorman.net/photos/2023/2023-02-16-new-artworking.jpg"/>
		
