        Rambling blog post alert: there isn&rsquo;t a simple, straightforward way to tell the story of how I use Obsidian. This is going to be a bit of a winding post as I start to describe my setup and workflow. And there will be gaps because a) I don&rsquo;t have time to write an omnibus description of this and b) you don&rsquo;t want to read that anyway. I&rsquo;ve been meaning to write this for awhile, but kept getting stuck by the scale of what was needed.
